    section(id='vendor-code-of-conduct-sanctions')

        h1 Sanctions
        p.
            Violations of the terms of this Addendum will result in sanctions found in the Member Code of
            Conduct as well as potential further sanctions and consequences as detailed here at the
            discretion of NCAS vendor relations or security staff.
      
        ul
            li.
                Revocation of vendor agreement without refund or further payment.
            li.
                Removal of products, services, or advertisements from any event spaces that do not
                meet code of conduct, event rule restrictions, or are illegal.

